
** Find the ns-server master using the orchestrator listed on UI log

** Get the nodeuuid-ip mapping from ns-server master(ns_server.debug.log)

[ns_server:debug,2017-08-08T15:54:19.114+05:30,ns_1@172.16.12.70:service_rebalancer-index-worker<0.24042.11>:service_rebalancer:rebalance:102]Got node infos:

** Search for ns_server.debug.log for service_rebalancer


** use rebalanceId to search in the logs

Rebalance protocol details
MB-45553


Setting redistribute index 

1. Enable redistribute index setting and wait for 10 seconds.

curl -X POST -u Administrator:password http://localhost:8091/settings/indexes -d redistributeIndexes=true
2. Trigger rebalance from CLI

./couchbase-cli rebalance -c http://localhost:8091 -u Administrator -p password
3. Disable redistribute index setting

curl -X POST -u Administrator:password http://localhost:8091/settings/indexes -d redistributeIndexes=false


